OL,3,CHead accountant jailed after stealing
OL,4,C#130k from own firm
OL,6,FMr Power said: "She deliberately
OL,7,Fomitted to record her overtime, and
OL,8,Finstead recorded the money in a
OL,9,Fseparate section that was for business
OL,10,Fuse and all aggregated together. So
OL,11,Fthe management account did not show
OL,12,Fany payment to her."
OL,14,FAfter Clarke's dismissal in 2019, the
OL,15,Fcompany embarked on an investigation
OL,16,Finto the petty cash, which would be
OL,17,Fused to reimburse colleagues for
OL,18,Fexpenses, as long as the receipt was
OL,19,Fprovided. Clarke had claimed large
OL,20,Fpayments for fuel using the petty cash.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
