OL,3,CHead accountant jailed after stealing
OL,4,C#130k from own firm
OL,6,FShe had also used the company credit
OL,7,Fcard, which she had access to from
OL,8,F2010 to 2019.
OL,10,FMr Power said: "The defendant's
OL,11,Fpayslips were recovered and examined
OL,12,Fand showed no repayments for the
OL,13,Fcredit card payments.
OL,15,F"There were very large payments spent
OL,16,Fon the credit card and and it was
OL,17,Fnever repaid."
