OL,4,C#130k from own firm
OL,6,FIn a statement, the company said it
OL,7,Fspent up to #80,000 pursuing the
OL,8,Finvestigation, which cost them a great
OL,9,Fdeal of time and effort. They also
OL,10,Fsaid it affected the time they had to
OL,11,Fconcentrate on customers and growing
OL,12,Fthe business.
OL,14,FMitigating, Rebecca Penfold, said
OL,15,FClarke suffered with her health, as a
OL,16,Fresult of having a stroke in 2024 and
OL,17,Fa diagnoses of chronic pancreatitis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
