OL,4,C#130k from own firm
OL,6,FMs Penfold said Clarke had put her
OL,7,Ffamily home up for sale with the
OL,8,Fintent of the proceeds being used to
OL,9,Frecompense the company.
OL,11,FShe said: "The reason why she
OL,12,Fcommitted the offence was for a better
OL,13,Flife for her daughter - it was a gross
OL,14,Ferror on her part... She says how very
OL,15,Fsorry she is for what happened."
