OL,6,FJailing Clarke, of Elm Tree Road,
OL,7,FBredbury, for 21 months, Judge Kevin
OL,8,FSlack said: "This was sustained fraud
OL,9,Fon a large scale. I am told you are
OL,10,Fremorseful, but you have spent many
OL,11,Fmonths if not years of burying your
OL,12,Fhead in the sand."
